The paper deals with a visual grounding task that involves natural language processing and computer vision. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the proposed task involves machine learning algorithms, which suggests that it could also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
